    dc:description "Figs. 1–3. Socotran Colydinae. 1–2. Sprecodes socotrensis sp. nov. (1 – habitus in dorsal view; 2 – same in ventral aspect). 3 – Lasconotus hajeki sp. nov., habitus in dorsal view." ;
